Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.80,0:01:48.15,Default1,46,0000,0000,0000,,餘寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.15,0:01:57.95,Default5,46,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}慶祝完新年一月過後, 已經是二月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.15,0:02:09.75,Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}從家裡搬出去後, 不知不覺中已經過了一個半月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.45,0:02:15.05,Default5,48,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在這段時間中努力讓自己將注意力集中在工作上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.05,0:02:19.05,Default5,49,0000,0000,0000,,最受歡迎的仍然是義大利料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.55,Default5,50,0000,0000,0000,,中式料理要用轉盤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.25,Default5,51,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}其實, 工作是我唯一擁有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.15,0:02:28.15,Default5,52,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不讓腦袋去想多餘的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.15,Default5,53,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}並且為做一個身心健全的社會人而生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.45,0:02:33.65,Default5,54,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.85,Default5,55,0000,0000,0000,,午安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.55,Default5,56,0000,0000,0000,,您好, 正等著妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.15,Default5,57,0000,0000,0000,,對不起遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.65,Default5,58,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.85,Default5,59,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}進行得不如想像中的順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.45,Default5,61,0000,0000,0000,,我借妳計程車錢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.25,Default5,62,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎, 好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.35,0:03:54.95,Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}結果到了最後, 那天結束後我所想的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.95,Default5,64,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}哥哥, 你還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.95,Default5,65,0000,0000,0000,,早安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.75,Default5,66,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}有好好地吃飯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.65,Default5,67,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}沒有感冒吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:38.95,Default5,68,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我想了很多關於我的想法, 哥哥的想法還有那之後的許多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.95,0:04:42.85,Default5,69,0000,0000,0000,,和我無緣的那天又要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.85,Default5,70,0000,0000,0000,,七夏妳也還沒有男朋友吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.05,0:04:45.95,Default5,71,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.65,Default5,72,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.95,Default5,73,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 七夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.65,Default5,74,0000,0000,0000,,妳在煩惱些什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.35,Default5,75,0000,0000,0000,,妳最近一直無精打彩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:05.65,Default5,76,0000,0000,0000,,上次妳說要住我家的, 卻突然又回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.55,Default5,77,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.65,Default5,78,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.05,Default5,79,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.75,Default5,80,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.55,Default5,81,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.55,Default5,82,0000,0000,0000,,真是的, 妳不必隱瞞嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.25,Default5,83,0000,0000,0000,,不管是難過的事, 煩惱的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.25,Default5,84,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都可以跟我說呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:36.05,Default5,85,0000,0000,0000,,如果我幫得上忙的, 一定會幫妳的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.15,Default5,86,0000,0000,0000,,我想雙葉妳大概是不會瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.05,Default5,87,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.55,Default5,88,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.45,Default5,89,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.35,Default5,90,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不說我怎麼會瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.85,0:06:05.55,Default5,91,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是, 只有我一個人思考的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.05,Default5,92,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那無論如何也找不到答案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.95,Default5,93,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.45,Default5,94,0000,0000,0000,,妳呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.95,Default5,95,0000,0000,0000,,住我那是沒關係, 但是換洗衣物什麼的該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.95,Default5,96,0000,0000,0000,,我會先回家去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.45,Default5,97,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話妳就在家睡吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.55,Default5,98,0000,0000,0000,,可是, 你那裡離公司近嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.55,Default5,99,0000,0000,0000,,早上就能多睡一會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.55,Default5,100,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.25,0:06:38.05,Default5,101,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所以, 好幾次都走到哥哥的公司前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.75,Default5,102,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}也想去哥哥的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.45,Default5,103,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.75,0:07:08.85,Default5,104,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我們說好吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.35,Default5,105,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}今晚是最後一次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.35,Default5,106,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}別再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.75,Default5,107,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}想起哥哥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.25,Default5,108,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我就忍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.85,Default5,109,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.85,Default5,110,0000,0000,0000,,就吃這麼一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.35,Default5,111,0000,0000,0000,,妳最近好像沒什麼胃口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.25,Default5,112,0000,0000,0000,,嗯! 我飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.55,Default5,113,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是, 哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.25,Default5,114,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是不會對自己的感情說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.65,Default5,115,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我果然還是對哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.35,Default5,116,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.45,Default5,117,0000,0000,0000,,竟然六點就把我叫起來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.05,Default5,118,0000,0000,0000,,睡相不好全身痛死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.75,Default5,119,0000,0000,0000,,妳又住他家了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.25,Default5,120,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.25,Default5,121,0000,0000,0000,,找死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.25,0:08:38.75,Default5,122,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳老是住他家, 他怎麼會有機會帶女孩子回家呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.75,Default5,123,0000,0000,0000,,我不也是女孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.35,Default5,124,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個理由才一直住他家的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.25,Default5,125,0000,0000,0000,,你認為呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.75,Default5,126,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.45,Default5,127,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.45,0:08:53.75,Default5,128,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎突然開始一個人住的原因啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.55,Default5,129,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛! 是有什麼事吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.25,Default5,130,0000,0000,0000,,家裡的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.35,0:08:59.95,Default5,131,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.95,0:09:05.55,Default5,132,0000,0000,0000,,聞了七夏的內衣而被趕出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.55,Default5,133,0000,0000,0000,,他又不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.95,0:09:13.25,Default5,134,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}如果我說正是如此\N他們會有什麼表情呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.25,0:09:18.95,Default5,135,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}聞了她的內衣, 邊想著她邊自慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.75,Default5,136,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}最後還抱住了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.85,Default5,137,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}為了阻止那樣的自己而搬離開家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.65,Default5,138,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}結果, 想的都是她的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.75,0:09:37.15,Default5,139,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}妳如果知道那樣子的我, 會怎麼想呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.65,Default5,140,0000,0000,0000,,別皺著一張臉嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.75,Default5,141,0000,0000,0000,,我本沒打算這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.05,Default5,142,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會忘記東西的嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.25,Default5,143,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.75,Default5,144,0000,0000,0000,,找到月票後我就馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.45,Default5,145,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說不能來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.45,0:09:59.95,Default5,146,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是你的女朋友, 多少能照顧你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.65,Default5,147,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.15,0:10:12.85,Default5,148,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會對女人沒興趣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.65,0:10:18.15,Default5,149,0000,0000,0000,,因為, 最近都沒聽到你的風流傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.95,Default5,150,0000,0000,0000,,今天也和小田切在說呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.65,Default5,151,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 等一下, 我去買煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.25,Default5,152,0000,0000,0000,,她在說什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.15,Default5,153,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 那不是七夏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.75,Default5,154,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.85,Default5,155,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.25,Default5,156,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:53.45,Default5,157,0000,0000,0000,,夠了喔! 奇怪耶! 你在想什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.45,0:11:56.95,Default5,158,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 真是的, 我的頭髮都亂了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.95,Default5,159,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 你說句話啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.45,Default5,160,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要躲七夏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.75,Default5,161,0000,0000,0000,,她走了唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.95,Default5,162,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎? 為什麼你要逃走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.15,0:12:16.75,Default5,163,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 耕四郎, 為什麼你要逃走啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.55,Default5,164,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎從家裡搬出來是因為七夏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.85,Default5,165,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.75,0:12:49.15,Default5,166,0000,0000,0000,,算了, 家務事也是有很多種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.45,Default5,167,0000,0000,0000,,小田切也在擔心你唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.75,Default5,168,0000,0000,0000,,還說你是不是聞了妹妹的內衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.65,Default5,169,0000,0000,0000,,或是襲擊了熟睡中的妹妹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.25,Default5,170,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是很認真的說著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.55,Default5,171,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.85,Default5,172,0000,0000,0000,,在變成那樣之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.85,Default5,173,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛認真了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.75,Default5,174,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.65,0:13:25.35,Default5,175,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起來, 覺得你們不像兄妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.55,Default5,176,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間瀰漫著奇怪的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.55,0:13:32.55,Default5,177,0000,0000,0000,,如果那麼親密, 就不會分開了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.25,Default5,178,0000,0000,0000,,七夏又這麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.55,Default5,179,0000,0000,0000,,之前也說過, 你給她的感覺與其說是哥哥\N倒不如說是王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.25,Default5,180,0000,0000,0000,,七夏看你的眼神都在發亮呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.25,Default5,181,0000,0000,0000,,你對妹妹出手了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.95,Default5,182,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.15,Default5,183,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼? 她是你妹妹耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.55,Default5,184,0000,0000,0000,,你不為她的人生著想嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.15,Default5,185,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.65,Default5,186,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.25,Default5,187,0000,0000,0000,,所以, 我才在那樣之前搬了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.25,Default5,188,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.85,Default5,189,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.65,Default5,190,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定要說成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.45,0:14:20.55,Default5,191,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不知道...一開始我們就是兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.65,Default5,192,0000,0000,0000,,噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.55,Default5,193,0000,0000,0000,,真覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.05,Default5,194,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.05,Default5,195,0000,0000,0000,,都這把年紀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.05,0:14:45.65,Default5,196,0000,0000,0000,,對妹妹...而且還是親生妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.95,Default5,197,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.95,0:14:48.95,Default5,198,0000,0000,0000,,差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.05,Default5,199,0000,0000,0000,,變態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.35,0:15:09.35,Default5,200,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}沒錯, 結果就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.35,0:15:12.45,Default5,201,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}很久以前我就應該知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.35,Default5,202,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.65,Default5,203,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}這種感覺是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.15,0:16:17.05,Default5,204,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我...果然還是喜歡哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.55,0:16:30.05,Default5,205,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所以, 我想見哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.75,Default5,206,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.55,Default5,207,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.05,Default5,208,0000,0000,0000,,聽說不舒服請假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.15,Default5,209,0000,0000,0000,,打電話的聲音像快死了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.55,Default5,210,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.95,Default5,211,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是知道些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.05,Default5,212,0000,0000,0000,,嗯! 病得很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.95,Default5,213,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說, 妳昨晚沒住他家吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.15,Default5,214,0000,0000,0000,,也許他好不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.45,Default5,215,0000,0000,0000,,耶? 那...那麼嚴重?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.55,Default5,216,0000,0000,0000,,那個懦夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.15,0:17:26.05,Default5,217,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}很可惜, 沒能聽到加奈子的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.65,Default5,218,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那表示那還不是確定的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.65,Default5,219,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯! 確實是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.65,Default5,220,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}只是傳聞而已吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.15,Default5,221,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.65,Default5,222,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那麼她也無法給你任何意見吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.45,Default5,223,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但是, 能不能就稍微透露一些呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.85,Default5,224,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}透露一些? 如果真要結婚, 在這種敏感時刻, 會被說閒話的, 對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.75,Default5,225,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不只是名人, 你不認為嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.25,Default5,226,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我不知道該說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.85,Default5,227,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這種事情, 我相信妳比我還更了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.85,0:17:57.55,Default5,228,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但這關係到採訪的廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.95,Default5,229,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大概她懷孕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.95,Default5,230,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我也聽到了這樣的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.95,0:18:06.55,Default5,231,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她最近取消了連續劇的演出, 對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.95,Default5,232,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}知道原因嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.45,Default5,233,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她說她的身體不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.75,Default5,234,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不管如何, 這似乎是個慶幸的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.65,Default5,235,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.95,Default5,236,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.85,0:20:01.25,Default5,237,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我...在期待什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.35,Default5,238,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}無法下定決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.75,Default5,239,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}也無法死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:21.25,Default5,240,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}從她身邊逃走, 也從公司裡逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.85,Default5,241,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}無論哪邊都不是徹底完整的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.95,Default5,242,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在這張可鄙的臉之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.25,Default5,243,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我...到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:48.05,Default5,244,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見妳呀...
